title: Amazing Achievements Of A Young Social And Internet Entrepreneur
text:
IN People ON 26 Feb, 2017 Amazing Achievements Of A Young Social And Internet Entrepreneur Share on twitter Follow Us On 
It is not very often that we come across someone as young and inspiring as Mohit Kumar Tripathi . A young boy from Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh who has a lot to be proud of- Organizations, firms, and a lot of awards. His wisdom screams when he says, "I know why I am here and my only real focused goal is to live each day to the fullest and to try and honour God and be an encouragement to others. What the future holds is firmly in God's hands, and I am very happy about that!" Amazing Achievements Of A Young Social And Internet Entrepreneur 754 396
